column2: SELECT    m.Name AS Name_cls,n.objid, n.distance, o.ra AS ra, o.dec AS dec,    o.modelMag_u as mu, o.modelMag_g as mg, o.modelMag_r as mr, o.modelMag_i as mi, o.modelMag_z as mz,    c.z as MEDIAN_Z, c.zErr as SIGMA_Z,    ISNULL(s.z,#) as z,ISNULL(s.zErr,#) as zErr,    o.score as score  FROM MyDB.maughan_may_# AS m    CROSS APPLY dbo.fGetNearbyObjAllEq( m.ra, m.dec, # ) AS n    left outer join SpecObj as s on o.objID = s.bestObjID    JOIN Galaxy AS o ON n.objid = o.objid    JOIN Photoz AS c ON c.objid = o.objid WHERE   c.z > # AND   ( (o.modelMag_g - o.modelMag_r) BETWEEN # AND #) AND   o.modelMag_g < # AND   o.score >= # AND   clean = # AND (calibStatus_r & #) != #
